The Security Council has unanimously reinforced sanctions against North Korea since 2006 in an attempt to stifle the financing of Pyongyang's nuclear and ballistic missile programmes.
Mr Pompeo met Mr Ri at the UN General Assembly and then said that he would visit Pyongyang again next month to prepare for a second summit.
Pompeo has visited North Korea three times this year, but his last trip did not go well.
